Olalem lo Laitoriani


1  Nelotu ororei lo Laitoriani enatii aajoki: 
2  “Enkerai e tung'ani, intorioki enkomom ino enkalo e Yerusalem niliki ororei aarare nena wuejitin sinyat; imbonoki tigilunore enkop e Israel 
3  nijoki ina kop e Israel, Inji ejo Olaitoriani: Ing'ura ekaarare iyie, naa kaaitorioki iyie olalem lashutu te nchashur enye, nadung'oo tiatua iyie lelo supati o ltorrok. 
4  Ore amu kadung'oo te iyie lelo supati o lelo torrok, neaku kepuku olalem lai aing'uaa enchashur enye aarare iltung'ana pooki eiteru te kopikop o meshomo moikuape; 
5  neyiolou iltung'ana pooki aajo ara nanu Olaitoriani otushutua olalem lai te nchashur; nemeitokini aaigil aashukoki olalem enchashur. 
6  Iyagie naa, enkerai e tung'ani; iyagie oltau omu eeta osina to ltau le mion te dukuya nkonyek enye. 
7  Naa tinikinkilikuan ninche aajoki, ‘Ainyoo peyie iyagie?’ naa ijoki, ‘Te nkaraki lelo kiliku oopuonu. Ore peyie ebau, naa kelepori pooki tau ore nkaik pooki naa keshalu, ore pooki tau neiterre neshalu nkung pooki anaa enkare. Ing'ura, ajo elotu naa keitabari ninye.’ ” Ejo Olaitoriani Enkai.


8  Nelotu ororei lo Laitoriani enatii naajoki, 
9  “Enkerai e tung'ani, imbonisho nijo, Ena ejo Olaitoriani:

Olalem, eiyioki olalem,

neiutuutoki aasik,


10  aaii tenkaraki eyieng'are,

netisikaki meimerlela anaa enkiwuang'ata!

Arashu aikintobiru enkuenia?

Itemenayie eng'udi, enkerai ai,

o pooki toki e nchata.


11  Metaa eishooyioki olalem metisiki,

peyie etumi aaibung'a

neiyioki nesiki,

peyie etumi aatipik ina aina oloyieng'isho.


12  Inchira niyietu nakerai e tung'ani,

amu kegilunore ninye iltung'ana laainei;

kegilunore ninye iltung'ana pooki kituaak le Israel;

etipikaki ninche pooki olalem tenebo iltung'ana laainei.

Toosho naa enkupes ino.


13  Amu meaku ninye entemata

kaa eas ninye tinimenaa iyie engudi?”

ejo Olaitoriani Enkai.


14  “Imbonisho naa, enkerai e tung'ani, toosho inkaik inono nincho olalem meeu adou katitin are, ee kat uni, ilo alem le lelo ooari metuata; olalem leyieng'are kitok, laa ninye oman ninche, 
15  peyie etum iltauja lenye aatalepori, nebatata ilkumok too nkishomin enye. Aishorua ilo alem oimerlel; Aha! eitobiruno ninye anaa enkiwuang'ata, netisikaki peyie etum ateyiengisho. 
16  Tudung'o oleng tatene o kedienye ine wueji netuutakaki enepi olalem. 
17  Ekaosh sii nanu nkaik aainei, naa kaitaraposh engoro ai; nanu Olaitoriani oiroro.”

Olalem lo laiguanani le Babilon


18  Neitoki ororei lo Laitoriani alotu enatii naajoki: 
19  “Enkerai e tung'ani, tuutu inkoitoi are tenkaraki ilo alem le ilo aiguanani le Babilon olotu; epuonu pokira are teina kop. Nintobiriri embao nautu eneimi, nipik ninye dukuya ina oitoi nalo enkanasa; 
20  tuutu enkoitoi naim ilo alem alo Raba oo Lamoni o meshomo Yuda o meshomo Yerusalem ina ang nasheta isunta. 
21  Amu eitasho olaiguanani le Babilon teine neorore inkoitoi te rishata e nena oitoi are, easishore enaibon; neikirikirie mbaa, neikilikuanishore enkitanyaanyukoto e nkai naji Terafi, neing'or emonyua eina ngues naibonishore. 
22  Ore atua enkaina enye e tatene nepuku enkukuo e Yerusalem pee ebol enkutuk enye te nkishirata, peyie eilepie oltoilo te mbuaata, pee eitorioki isekenke naagilieki nkishomin neitasheyie nenen neesheta te ng'olon neshetu iltaleta ooibung'ishore. 
23  Kake ore te ninche, netiu anaa enaibon elejare; einosa ninche ilmuma oogol; kake eyau ninye eng'oki enye metadamuni, peyie etumi aaibung'a.


24  “Metaa inji ejo Olaitoriani Enkai: Ore amu intaa ing'ok inono inaadamuni, te ina nemeekure eisudoroyu intorrok inono, neaku ore too siaaitin inono pooki naa keibalayu ing'ok inono; amu ieuo iyie adamu; naa aikiya ninche iyie. 
25  Ore iyie, intae iltung'ana torrok lemesinya, olkitok le Israel, ilo oewuo enkolong enye, erishata enkitamioto ino nabayie, 
26  inji ejo Olaitoriani Enkai: Intayu enkarasha endukuya, nintayu ina maupe enkitoo; meitoki intokitin aatiu anaa enaikununo; isisa ina nidol etii abori, nintadou ina natii shumata. 
27  Enkidaata, enkidaata, kaitobiru nanu enkidaata; metumi ninye eneima ninye o meeu ninye aa enenye esipata; naa ninye aisho nanu.

Olalem tenebo Ilamoni


28   “Ore iyie, nakerai e tung'ani, imbonisho nijo: Inji ejo Olaitoriani Enkai tialo Ilamoni, neipirta sii enkurruna enye; tejo, Olalem, olalem etushurtuaki peyie eyieng'ishoi, netisikaki meimerlela anaa enkiwuang'ata, 
29  ore edol ninche te ntae induaat elejare ina kata eibonoki ninche intae elejare, peyie eeniki imurto e lelo tung'ana lemesinya torrok, lelo ootabaikia ninche enkolong enye enkata enkitamioto enye nabayie. 
30  Tushukoki olalem enchashur enye. Teine wueji nikintobirieki iyie, teina kop apa ning'uaa ekaaiguanare nanu iyie. 
31  Naa kabukoki shumata intae engoro ai; nakutaki intae enkima engoro ai; na kapik intae inkaik oo ltung'ana arruok meidaikie. 
32  Iakuku intae ilkeek le nkima; ore osarge linyi nejing empolos e ina kop; meitokini aekata aadamu intae; amu nanu Olaitoriani oiroro.”

